s.co.uk/railway-carriage-fenland/ |website=Railway Station Cottages |accessdate=28 April 2020}}</ref>\n* Wolkenstein, Germany.<ref name=\"wolken\">{{cite web |title=Herzlich willkommen im Wolkensteiner Zughotel! |url=https://wolkensteiner-zughotel.de/ |website=Das Wolkensteiner Zughotel |accessdate=28 April 2020 |language=German}}</ref>\n\n===Railway inspired accommodation===\nOther railway based, or inspired, accommodation includes:{{Expand list|date=April 2020}}\n* [[Aberystwyth Cliff Railway]] Apartment, Ceredigion.<ref>{{cite web |title=Cliff Railway Apartment |url=https://www.cottages.com/cottages/cliff-railway-apartment-cc621043 |website=Cottages.com |accessdate=28 April 2020}}</ref>\n* Akeld, Northumberland.<ref>{{cite web |title=The Guards Van |url=https://www.quirkyaccom.com/the-guards-van|website=Quirky Accom - The Directory of Unusual Places to Stay |accessdate=27 April 2020}}</ref>\n* {{rws|Bardon Mill}}, [[Northumberland]], a converted waiting room.<ref>{{cite web |title=Bardon Mill Waiting Room |url=https://www.cottages.com/cottages/bardon-mill-waiting-room-cc334063 |website=Cottages.com |accessdate=28 April 2020}}</ref>\n* Berwyn Stationmaster House, Denbishire.<ref>{{cite web |title=Berwyn Stationmaster House |url=http://www.llangollen-railway.co.uk/holiday-let/ |website=Llangollen Railway |accessdate=27 April 2020}}</ref>\n* {{rws|Betws-y-Coed}} station apartment.<ref>{{cite web |title=Snowdonia Station Apartment |url=http://www.betws-y-coed.co.uk/accommodation/item/69953/Snowdonia_Station_Apartment.html |website=Betws-y-Coed and District Tourism Information and Accommodation |accessdate=28 April 2020}}</ref>\n* Dahn-Reichenbach, Germany, station accommodation.<ref name=\"reich\" />\n* {{rws|Dunrobin Castle}}, Sutherland.<ref>{{cite web |title=Dunrobin Castle Station |url=http://www.scotlandrailholiday.com/dunrobin/index.htm |website=Dunrobin Castle |accessdate=27 April 2020}}</ref>\n* Durbin, West Virginia, converted cabooses.<ref>{{cite web |title